data.title: Populuslog: People Information Database: Abstract-Information About Individuals On Publicly Available Web
data.meta_description: PopulusLog.ISCIS09 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. In this paper, we present populuslog, a novel web data mining system. It involves a framework for tools that collect, extract, mine, query, browse, and visualize information. PopulusLog is a pioneering example of next generation search engines.
